text.tspan: Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem. It combines information on voting rights, the
freedom and fairness of elections, freedoms of association and expression, civil liberties, and executive
constraints. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most democratic).
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13)
